t a transfer measurement; RT-7a transfer needs kernel-covered external items (f2b-TRANSFER, gated)","tag":"MEASURED"},{"claim":"greedy attempt-0 decode + fixed resample seeds make the pipeline deterministic given the pinned models; a same-items rerun of the logged F2 500 would have zero evidential value — the fresh item set is the entire point of this experiment","tag":"STIPULATED"},{"claim":"coverage disclosure (mandatory): kernel-expressibility coverage 0.3542 at rung molecules-v0, MEASURED by m0b on one incomplete kernel-v0 instance — NOT general coverage; every accuracy claim is bounded to the kernel-covered slice","tag":"MEASURED"},{"claim":"planning constants (throughput tok/s, chars/token, 2x overhead) are dry-plan ESTIMATES only and are never emitted as measurements","tag":"STIPULATED"},{"claim":"supersedes-in-spirit: this record registers the G-13 promotion path for the quarantined (R1,R3) exploratory estimand of poc/f2/f2b-reanalysis.md; NOTHING here amends f2 — the frozen F2 record, its FAIL verdict and its confirmatory secondaries stand exactly as issued","tag":"BINDING-NOTE"}],"bootstrap_B":10000,"dropped_arms":"R2, the k-ladder (single fixed pre-registered k=4), the gold-oracle diagnostic ceiling, all cascades (HE2 failed confirmatory in F2; not re-litigated without a design change), int4, RAG, self-consistency — advisor right-size; their F2 confirmatory readings stand","fresh_items":"data/d-qa-r (built 2026-07-09, generator seed dqar/1|f2b-replicate|20260709): 1000 items over the 108 covered concepts; ID-disjoint (dqar: namespace) AND full-prompt-surface-disjoint from all 650 logged d-qa items (leak rule LC8, fail-closed); NOT a rerun of the logged 500 — deterministic decode would reproduce them. ADVISOR RIGHT-SIZE (2026-07-09): the run evaluates a fixed deterministic prefix of the rank-sorted covered set, per_arm_items=250; the full 1000-item corpus stays on disk with its pinned kot-corpus-hash (no corpus re-pin) and every subset item is fresh + disj